52
00:01:59,978 --> 00:02:02,054
<font color="#ffff00">Tapi aku tak pernah suka
dengan nama Juanita.</font>

53
00:02:02,056 --> 00:02:03,739
<font color="#ffff00">Kalian bisa memanggilku Princess.</font>

54
00:02:03,741 --> 00:02:05,499
<font color="#ffff00">Kenapa Princess?</font>

55
00:02:05,501 --> 00:02:08,394
<font color="#ffff00">Karena "Queen"
