<font color="#ffff00">Tidak! Tidak!</font>

83
00:03:29,744 --> 00:03:31,401
<font color="#ffff00">Sial.</font>

84
00:03:32,588 --> 00:03:35,314
<font color="#ffff00">Maaf soal itu.</font>

85
