131
00:06:10,665 --> 00:06:12,654
<font color="#ffff00">tapi aku tak yakin
aku mempercayai kalian.</font>

132
00:06:12,656 --> 00:06:14,656
<font color="#ffff00">Maksudku, aku kalah jumlah.</font>

133
00:06:14,658 --> 00:06:16,558
<font color="#ffff00">Aku mungkin bisa membunuh
