159
00:08:41,288 --> 00:08:43,063
<font color="#ffff00">Biar aku saja.</font>

160
00:08:43,065 --> 00:08:45,640
<font color="#ffff00">Jangan pulang.</font>

161
00:08:45,642 --> 00:08:48,068
<font color="#ffff00">Mereka akan menemukan kita
