162
00:08:48,070 --> 00:08:50,887
<font color="#ffff00">Kami punya rencana untuk mengakhiri ini.</font>

163
00:08:50,889 --> 00:08:52,531
<font color="#ffff00">Salah satunya mungkin yang kau sukai.</font>

164
00:08:55,393 --> 00:08:57,060
<font color="#ffff00">Dalam pelarian seperti ini,</font>

165
00:08:57,062 --> 00:08:59,972
<font color="#ffff00">hampir saja...</font>

166
00:08:59,974 --> 00:09:04,309
<font color="#ffff00">...mengingatkanku pada teman lama.</font>

167
00:09:04,311 --> 00:09:06,495
<font color="#ffff00">Sepertinya sudah lama sekali sekarang.</font>

168
00:09:09,741 --> 00:09:11,500
<font color="#ffff00">Michonne?</font>

169
00:09:11,502 --> 00:09:16,096
<font color="#ffff00">Kau bisa mendengarku?</font>

170
00:09:16,098 --> 00:09:18,223
<font color="#ffff00">Michonne?</font>

171
00:09:55,638 --> 00:09:58,955
<font color="#ffff00">Tak ada tanda-tanda mereka.
Mereka pergi cepat sekali.</font>

172
