<font color="#ffff00">Tak mungkin mereka pergi jauh.</font>

173
00:10:00,643 --> 00:10:03,644
<font color="#ffff00">Apa kita akan mencari di tempat lain?</font>

174
00:10:03,646 --> 00:10:05,220
<font color="#ffff00">Dimana...</font>

175
00:10:05,222 --> 00:10:07,797
<font color="#ffff00"><i> Mereka tak punya apa-apa... </i></font>

176
